er Olympic Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2026_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2026_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"score\": 0.9999355642413921, \"rank\": 6.44399081751206e-05, \"text\": \"Milan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\"}, {\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6004117919421956, \"rank\": 0.6655215209131873, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Elsa/Getty Images)  It was donated after the game by the International Ice Hockey Federation.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1170, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_the_lioness\", \"score\": 0.5000224932040783, \"rank\": 0.5590800203536322, \"text\": \"Elsa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_the_lioness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_the_lioness\"}, {\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999999962710717, \"rank\": 2.248104157637067e-09, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Ice_Hockey_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Ice Hockey Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Ice_Hockey_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Ice_Hockey_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately, in the easiest words, it was never Jack's puck to own,\\\" Philip Pritchard, vice president of the resource center and curator for the Hockey Hall of Fame,told ESPNin response to Hughes.\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.6317368863445635, \"rank\": 0.5819292968082649, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}, {\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9770148725205324, \"rank\": 0.023481967553159084, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been donated to us now.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For every artifact that's been donated, we have a paper trail and signed paperwork of where it's come from.\\\"\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NHL playersare often allowed to keep pucks and gear for themselves for milestone moments in NHL games, but in most international tournaments, including the Olympics, an on-ice official is in charge of collecting what becomes memorabilia and giving it to an off-ice official for identification, who will then deliver it to the IIHF for donation.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999992387529, \"rank\": 7.594045534764767e-10, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999992387529, \"rank\": 7.594045534764767e-10, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA men's hockey gold medalists have irked liberal pundits and news organizations despite captivating the nation with their Olympic accomplishment.\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999927831595, \"rank\": 7.2167310187708495e-09, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(AP Photo/Luca Bruno)  JACK HUGHES REFLECTS ON NEWFOUND FAME SINCE OLYMPICS, INCLUDING SUPPORT FROM RIVAL FANS  \\\"Items are formally transferred to the Hall through IIHF's established artifact donation process and added into our permanent collection.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 1.5780664825724192e-12, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These artifacts are preserved, exhibited and shared with fans worldwide through our museum and international outreach programs, ensuring that defining Olympic and World Championship moments are preserved and remain accessible to the global hockey community,\\\" the Hall of Fame said in a statement.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Hall of Fame had staff on hand in Milan to assist in the donation process.\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2689, \"end\": 2694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"score\": 0.9999355642413921, \"rank\": 6.44399081751206e-05, \"text\": \"Milan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Megan Keller's golden goal, scored three days before Hughes', is also in the Hall of Fame.\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2730, \"end\": 2742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\", \"score\": 0.9999993486210162, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Megan Keller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Keller\"}, {\"begin\": 2783, \"end\": 2789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9770148725205324, \"rank\": 0.023481967553159084, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would not even want it for myself,\\\" Hughes explained.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2861, \"end\": 2867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9770148725205324, \"rank\": 0.023481967553159084, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd want it for my dad.\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know he'd just love, love having it.\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I look back in time in my career, I do not collect too many things for myself, but my dad's a monster collector for the three of us.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know he would have a special place for it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jack Hughes of the United States celebrates with the U.S. flag after scoring his second goal in overtime to win gold Feb. 22, 2026.\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3128, \"end\": 3132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.6317368863445635, \"rank\": 0.5819292968082649, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}, {\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9770148725205324, \"rank\": 0.023481967553159084, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 3147, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5964914143215882e-12, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3181, \"end\": 3190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999058673, \"rank\": 9.422338382264735e-11, \"text\": \"U.S. flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org